                                    - Publish post from already markdown file to Viblo.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
                        <div class="item">
                            <img
                                class="item__image"
                                src="~/assets/images/viblo-atom-plugin/atom-03.png"
                                alt="Viblo atom plugin - Manage your gallery"
                            />
                            <div class="item__body">
                                <h4 class="title">Manage your gallery</h4>
                                <p>
                                    Upload your images from Atom to Viblo, <br>
                                    or delete your uploaded images.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
                        <div class="item">
                            <img
                                class="item__image"
                                src="~/assets/images/viblo-atom-plugin/atom-01.png"
